Module org.panteleyev.freedesktop
Package org.panteleyev.freedesktop.menu

Enum Class Category

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Category>
org.panteleyev.freedesktop.menu.Category
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Category>, Constable
public enum Category extends Enum<Category>
Menu Categories. The list of Main Categories consist of those categories that every conforming desktop environment MUST support. By including one of these categories in an application's desktop entry file the application will be ensured that it will show up in a section of the application menu dedicated to this category.
